comments.body: the speckled rattlesnake diversity in the area is remarkable
Estimada @agatica  muchas gracias! Espero sean de su agrado :)

Hi @blevine This species used to be C. mitchelli, but with new taxonomical studies, resulted a new species. The NOM-059 says that when a species splited in other species, those new species mantaing the same status, but that need to be added into iNat.
Hola Jorge, ahhh  ok, buen saber. Gracias por el info.
@blevine thank you! it was a good experience travel to the island, found and photograph this amazing snake.
